quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  6,132,Kwa aliyense kudzaperekedwa gawo molingana ndi zimene adachita. Sikuti Ambuye wako sadziwa zimene iwo achita
  6,133,"Ambuye wako ndi wolemera ndiponso ndi wachisoni ndipo ngati Iye afuna, akhoza kukuonongani ndi kuika m’malo mwanu ena amene Iye wafuna monga momwe Iye adakulengerani inu kuchokera ku mbeu ya anthu ena"
  6,134,Ndithudi chimene inu mukulonjezedwa chidzachitika ndipo inu simungachizembe ayi
  6,135,"Nena, “oh anthu anga! Chitani chimene mungachite, ndithudi, nanenso ndili kuchita chimene ndimachita ndipo inu mudzadziwa kuti ndani wa ife amene adzakhala ndi mapeto abwino m’moyo umene uli nkudza. Ndithudi anthu olakwa sadzapambana.”"
  6,136,"Ndipo iwo amaika pa mbali gawo la mbewu ndi gawo la ziweto kuti ndi za Mulungu ndipo amati: “Izi ndi za Mulungu pamene izi ndi za mafano athu.” Koma gawo limene amati ndi la mafano awo silifika kwa Mulungu ayi pamene gawo la Mulungu limafika lonse kwa mafano awo! Chiweruzo chawo ndi choipa kwambiri"
  6,137,"Motero kwa anthu opembedza mafano, mafano awo adapangitsa kupha ana awo kukhala chinthu chokondweretsa ndi cholinga chakuti awawononge iwo ndi kuwasokonezera chipembedzo chawo. Koma ngati Mulungu akadafuna, iwo sakadachita choncho. Motero asiyeni okha ndi zimene akupeka"